snippet.title: PUBG MOBILE - Royale Pass Season 8 Trailer
snippet.description: Are you ready to party on with PUBG MOBILE? Royale Pass Season 8 is out, and it's time for you to start completing missions, having fun, and earning rewards! Who will top the RP8 Leaderboards, will it be you?
